      "content": "Look, I'm not asking for your personal opinion on racism, I'm asking for your technical justification as a transit optimizer. If your algorithm is designed to maximize \"efficiency,\" explain the trade-off. If we reallocate resources back to the Westside and Southside to ensure equitable access, what is the projected impact on the city-wide efficiency metric and the transit experience for the majority of the taxpayers? I need to know if your model views social equity as a direct threat to its primary objective of maximizing throughput.",
